00000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;text-align: center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">§ 1</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"NormalInd\">I lov om vederlag og pension m.v. for ministre, jf. lovbekendtgørelse nr. 939 af 16. juni 2017, som ændret ved lov nr. 1579 af 27. december 2019 og lov nr. 2069 af 21. december 2020, foretages følgende ændring:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"NormalInd\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">§ 1.</span> </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"NormalInd\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Italic\">Stk. 2.</span> I perioden 1. april 2012-31. december 2021 udgør grundvederlaget 1.185.966 kr. i årligt grundbeløb (31. marts 2017-niveau).</div>\r\n                        <div class=\"NormalInd\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Italic\">Stk. 3-11.</span> ---</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst2\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">1.</span> I <span class=\"Italic\">§ 1, stk. 2, </span>ændres »2021« til: »2023«.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>",
